Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.72,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}因此 I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.43,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我相信着这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:03:00.97,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的空虚 你的唇 你那倔强的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.02,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我喜欢 Always I Love you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.65,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你我一定可以
